text-editor\" data-id=\"3e6f288\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-start=\"1990\" data-end=\"2024\"><strong data-start=\"1990\" data-end=\"2009\">Effective Date:<\/strong> October 2025<\/p><p data-start=\"2026\" data-end=\"2244\"><strong data-start=\"2026\" data-end=\"2042\">Eezy Booking<\/strong> respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our website or mobile application.<\/p><hr data-start=\"2246\" data-end=\"2249\" \/><h4 data-start=\"2251\" data-end=\"2284\"><strong data-start=\"2255\" data-end=\"2284\">1. Information We Collect<\/strong><\/h4><p data-start=\"2285\" data-end=\"2319\">We may collect the following data:<\/p><ul data-start=\"2320\" data-end=\"2570\"><li data-start=\"2320\" data-end=\"2405\"><p data-start=\"2322\" data-end=\"2405\"><strong data-start=\"2322\" data-end=\"2347\">Personal Information:<\/strong> Name, phone number, email address, and payment details.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"2406\" data-end=\"2478\"><p data-start=\"2408\" data-end=\"2478\"><strong data-start=\"2408\" data-end=\"2432\">Booking Information:<\/strong> Venue details, time, date, and preferences.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"2479\" data-end=\"2570\"><p data-start=\"2481\" data-end=\"2570\"><strong data-start=\"2481\" data-end=\"2500\">Technical Data:<\/strong> IP address, browser type, operating system, and device identifiers.<\/p><\/li><\/ul><hr data-start=\"2572\" data-end=\"2575\" \/><h4 data-start=\"2577\" data-end=\"2615\"><strong data-start=\"2581\" data-end=\"2615\">2. How We Use Your Information<\/strong><\/h4><p data-start=\"2616\" data-end=\"2644\">Your information is used to:<\/p><ul data-start=\"2645\" data-end=\"2871\"><li data-start=\"2645\" data-end=\"2683\"><p data-start=\"2647\" data-end=\"2683\">Process and confirm your bookings.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"2684\" data-end=\"2753\"><p data-start=\"2686\" data-end=\"2753\">Communicate important updates, reminders, and promotional offers.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"2754\" data-end=\"2807\"><p data-start=\"2756\" data-end=\"2807\">Enhance user experience and improve our platform.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"2808\" data-end=\"2871\"><p data-start=\"2810\" data-end=\"2871\">Ensure secure transactions and prevent fraudulent activity.<\/p><\/li><\/ul><hr data-start=\"2873\" data-end=\"2876\" \/><h4 data-start=\"2878\" data-end=\"2913\"><strong data-start=\"2882\" data-end=\"2913\">3. Data Protection Measures<\/strong><\/h4><ul data-start=\"2914\" data-end=\"3121\"><li data-start=\"2914\" data-end=\"3050\"><p data-start=\"2916\" data-end=\"3050\">Eezy Booking uses <strong data-start=\"2934\" data-end=\"2952\">SSL encryption<\/strong>, <strong data-start=\"2954\" data-end=\"2981\">secure payment gateways<\/strong>, and <strong data-start=\"2987\" data-end=\"3017\">firewall-protected servers<\/strong> to keep your information safe.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"3051\" data-end=\"3121\"><p data-start=\"3053\" data-end=\"3121\">We do <strong data-start=\"3059\" data-end=\"3087\">not sell, rent, or trade<\/strong> user data to any third parties.<\/p><\/li><\/ul><hr data-start=\"3123\" data-end=\"3126\" \/><h4 data-start=\"3128\" data-end=\"3151\"><strong data-start=\"3132\" data-end=\"3151\">4. Data Sharing<\/strong><\/h4><p data-start=\"3152\" data-end=\"3184\">We share limited data only with:<\/p><ul data-start=\"3185\" data-end=\"3391\"><li data-start=\"3185\" data-end=\"3244\"><p data-start=\"3187\" data-end=\"3244\"><strong data-start=\"3187\" data-end=\"3209\">Payment processors<\/strong> to complete secure transactions.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"3245\" data-end=\"3321\"><p data-start=\"3247\" data-end=\"3321\"><strong data-start=\"3247\" data-end=\"3286\">Venue partners or service providers<\/strong> to confirm and fulfill bookings.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"3322\" data-end=\"3391\"><p data-start=\"3324\" data-end=\"3391\"><strong data-start=\"3324\" data-end=\"3350\">Regulatory authorities<\/strong>, only when required by applicable law.<\/p><\/li><\/ul><hr data-start=\"3393\" data-end=\"3396\" \/><h4 data-start=\"3398\" data-end=\"3429\"><strong data-start=\"3402\" data-end=\"3429\">5. Cookies and Tracking<\/strong><\/h4><p data-start=\"3430\" data-end=\"3448\">We use cookies to:<\/p><ul data-start=\"3449\" data-end=\"3566\"><li data-start=\"3449\" data-end=\"3498\"><p data-start=\"3451\" data-end=\"3498\">Remember your preferences and login sessions.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"3499\" data-end=\"3566\"><p data-start=\"3501\" data-end=\"3566\">Analyze user activity to improve performance and functionality.<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p data-start=\"3568\" data-end=\"3669\">Users can disable cookies through browser settings, though this may affect some features of the site.<\/p><hr data-start=\"3671\" data-end=\"3674\" \/><h4 data-start=\"3676\" data-end=\"3698\"><strong data-start=\"3680\" data-end=\"3698\">6. Your Rights<\/strong><\/h4><p data-start=\"3699\" data-end=\"3732\">As a user, you have the right to:<\/p><ul data-start=\"3733\" data-end=\"3880\"><li data-start=\"3733\" data-end=\"3783\"><p data-start=\"3735\" data-end=\"3783\">Access, correct, or delete your personal data.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"3784\" data-end=\"3834\"><p data-start=\"3786\" data-end=\"3834\">Withdraw consent for marketing communications.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"3835\" data-end=\"3880\"><p data-start=\"3837\" data-end=\"3880\">Request details of how your data is used.<\/p><\/li><\/ul><hr data-start=\"3882\" data-end=\"3885\" \/><h5 data-start=\"3887\" data-end=\"3912\"><strong data-start=\"3891\" data-end=\"3912\">7. Policy Updates<\/strong><\/h5><p data-start=\"3913\" data-end=\"4082\">This Privacy Policy may be updated periodically to reflect changes in our practices. The updated version will be posted on this page with a revised <strong data-start=\"4061\" data-end=\"4082\"