we,\u201d \u201cour,\u201d or \u201cus\u201d) provides an online platform that allows users to discover, schedule, and book venues, events, or other related services.<br data-start=\"864\" data-end=\"867\" \/>By creating an account or making a booking through Eezy Booking, you agree to follow these terms and any future updates we make.<\/p><p data-start=\"997\" data-end=\"1087\">If you do not agree with these Terms &amp; Conditions, please refrain from using our services.<\/p><hr data-start=\"1089\" data-end=\"1092\" \/><h4 data-start=\"1094\" data-end=\"1115\"><strong data-start=\"1097\" data-end=\"1115\">2. Eligibility<\/strong><\/h4><p data-start=\"1116\" data-end=\"1146\">To use Eezy Booking, you must:<\/p><ul data-start=\"1147\" data-end=\"1357\"><li data-start=\"1147\" data-end=\"1222\"><p data-start=\"1149\" data-end=\"1222\">Be at least <strong data-start=\"1161\" data-end=\"1177\">18 years old<\/strong>, or have permission from a legal guardian.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"1223\" data-end=\"1277\"><p data-start=\"1225\" data-end=\"1277\">Provide accurate personal and payment information.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"1278\" data-end=\"1357\"><p data-start=\"1280\" data-end=\"1357\">Agree to comply with all local laws and regulations while using our platform.<\/p><\/li><\/ul><hr data-start=\"1359\" data-end=\"1362\" \/><h4 data-start=\"1364\" data-end=\"1387\"><strong data-start=\"1367\" data-end=\"1387\">3. User Accounts<\/strong><\/h4><ul data-start=\"1388\" data-end=\"1675\"><li data-start=\"1388\" data-end=\"1492\"><p data-start=\"1390\" data-end=\"1492\">Users are responsible for maintaining the <strong data-start=\"1432\" data-end=\"1451\">confidentiality<\/strong> of their account details and password.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"1493\" data-end=\"1568\"><p data-start=\"1495\" data-end=\"1568\">Any activity under your account will be considered your responsibility.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"1569\" data-end=\"1675\"><p data-start=\"1571\" data-end=\"1675\">If unauthorized use or suspicious activity occurs, notify us immediately at <strong data-start=\"1647\" data-end=\"1674\"><a class=\"decorated-link cursor-pointer\" rel=\"noopener\" data-start=\"1649\" data-end=\"1672\">support@eezybooking.com<\/a><\/strong>.<\/p><\/li><\/ul><hr data-start=\"1677\" data-end=\"1680\" \/><h4 data-start=\"1682\" data-end=\"1712\"><strong data-start=\"1685\" data-end=\"1712\">4. Booking and Payments<\/strong><\/h4><ul data-start=\"1713\" data-end=\"2058\"><li data-start=\"1713\" data-end=\"1809\"><p data-start=\"1715\" data-end=\"1809\">All bookings made through Eezy Booking are subject to <strong data-start=\"1769\" data-end=\"1785\">availability<\/strong> and <strong data-start=\"1790\" data-end=\"1806\">confirmation<\/strong>.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"1810\" data-end=\"1893\"><p data-start=\"1812\" data-end=\"1893\">Users must pay the total amount displayed at checkout to confirm their booking.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"1894\" data-end=\"1991\"><p data-start=\"1896\" data-end=\"1991\">Eezy Booking uses <strong data-start=\"1914\" data-end=\"1953\">secure third-party payment gateways<\/strong>. We do not store your card details.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"1992\" data-end=\"2058\"><p data-start=\"1994\" data-end=\"2058\">Bookings cannot be transferred or resold without prior approval.<\/p><\/li><\/ul><hr data-start=\"2060\" data-end=\"2063\" \/><h4 data-start=\"2065\" data-end=\"2100\"><strong data-start=\"2068\" data-end=\"2100\">5. Cancellations and Refunds<\/strong><\/h4><ul data-start=\"2101\" data-end=\"2346\"><li data-start=\"2101\" data-end=\"2179\"><p data-start=\"2103\" data-end=\"2179\">Cancellation and refund requests are handled as per our <strong data-start=\"2159\" data-end=\"2176\">Refund Policy<\/strong>.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"2180\" data-end=\"2252\"><p data-start=\"2182\" data-end=\"2252\">Refund eligibility depends on cancellation timing and partner terms.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"2253\" data-end=\"2346\">